{"tid":39173,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"有無 Minolta Fans？","createTime":"2016-12-14T11:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T17:01:56.000Z","uid":63282,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e842dcf3444a88d98944af6a9ccafd382ea1ac","tid":39173,"uid":63282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T11:52:18.000Z","msg":"自從舊年買咗 Sony A7RII 之後，入手 LA-EA4 並購入 Beercan，先開始認識 Minolta。可惜為時已晚，Minolta 已經俾 Sony 收咗皮。唯有喺 eBay 逐枝逐枝收，最近仲入埋 Dynax 7。有無 Minolta 同好埋嚟吹下水？<br />\n<br />\n已入手 AF 鏡頭如下：<br />\n2.8/24mm<br />\n2.8/28mm<br />\n3.5-4.5/24-105mm D<br />\n4/35-70mm<br />\n3.5-4.5/35-70mm<br />\n1.4/50mm<br />\n2.8/50mm Macro<br />\n2.8/100mm Macro<br />\n4/70-210mm (Beercan)<br />\n4.5-5.6/75-300mm (Big Beercan)<br />\n2.8/80-200mm APO G<br />\n<br />\n非 show off，只想與同好互相交流鏡頭心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23feaad4ebb17d8bc97bd487689083af6de9c3a7","tid":39173,"uid":7955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:27:41.000Z","msg":"Minolta 50/1.4 PG　<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd9ca26be7922ecf43f8390c759903600d0f30f","tid":39173,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:17:58.000Z","msg":"玩開md mount<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c66af1077a5dafb72a971cc9c78d9833e94b0b3","tid":39173,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:23:17.000Z","msg":"有支MC 58.4 PF 同MC 28mm F/2.8<br />\n<br />\nbid緊支MD 35.8同MD 24/2.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27fe2c4b08a544c2f3b19a7a96d1e62fe295bbd","tid":39173,"uid":63282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:06:25.000Z","msg":"其實 MD 同 AF 嘅光學質素如何比較？<br />\n<br />\n我只有 AF 鏡，當初覺得有得玩舊鏡之餘又有 AF (雖然 A7 配 LA-EA 4 只有十幾點)，感覺好新奇，有如將三十年前嘅舊嘢重新復活一樣。但我收集 Minolta 舊鏡頭仍傾向收第一代，諗住第一代用嘅料會靚啲。<br />\n<br />\n我知 MD 手動鏡都有好多銘鏡，比起 AF 鏡於光學質素上係咪又優勝啲？"},{"pid":"7ae8c2c74beef6f0edffb9506dd8469715eb705c","tid":39173,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:10:12.000Z","msg":"LA-EA 4 都成千幾蚊個<br />\n用黎玩minolta AF有少少妹仔大過主人婆feel<br />\n所以暫時仲未落坑<br />\n<br />\n擁有既md mount鏡<br />\nMC 58 1.4 PF x2<br />\nMC 28 2.8<br />\nMC 28 3.5<br />\nMC 100 2.5"},{"pid":"4e3120ab17ecdf07a4ca5a8f9d7d59787ee99e74","tid":39173,"uid":63282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LA-EA 4 都成千幾蚊個<br />\n用黎玩minolta AF有少少妹仔大過主人婆feel<br />\n所以暫時仲未落坑<br />\n<br />\n擁有既md mount鏡<br />\nMC 58 1.4 PF x2<br />\nMC 28 2.8<br />\nMC 28 3.5<br />\nMC 100 2.5</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n喺 <a href=\"http://price.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fprice.com&d=bb6jU4LTtXFQNJXGdwV0qmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=44e3ee41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">price.com</a> 搵到最平樓上舖買，原來 MIJ，反而相機同鏡頭都喺泰國做，吹脹。<br />\n<br />\n一勞永逸啦，貪佢有 AF 都只有呢個選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5100626758bff60d87065525489545d5614a167f","tid":39173,"uid":3931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:52:44.000Z","msg":"minotla 500 reflex AF<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12726e5811011f7493ca68f628a4c72fc91d21da","tid":39173,"uid":63282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:58:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>minotla 500 reflex AF<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢枝銘鏡，世上唯一 reflex AF lenses <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4bc8b42b01d91c5b487e2baba785f5c8f02514","tid":39173,"uid":3224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T16:09:50.000Z","msg":"MC同MD 都玩過幾支平鏡<br />\n印象深啲既反而係md24 2.8天星<br />\n自己唔係太鍾意MC，太舊色水太淡，後期既MD色水濃返啲感覺岩我口味啲"},{"pid":"549f1408aed35887d0f31738f65f0f2c8e04136b","tid":39173,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:00:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>MC同MD 都玩過幾支平鏡<br />\n印象深啲既反而係md24 2.8天星<br />\n自己唔係太鍾意MC，太舊色水太淡，後期既MD色水濃返啲感覺岩我口味啲</blockquote><br />\n天星即係leica R 24/2.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c223b7d08059d3ab269079bb092d39e89e9ccbfd","tid":39173,"uid":9633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:33:29.000Z","msg":"35.8MC 正到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔捨得放"},{"pid":"b9eddf83781a6242d891d108d7464d18ac374af3","tid":39173,"uid":63282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:19:50.000Z","msg":"無人玩 Minolta A mount 鏡？"},{"pid":"027f0d02d67d2cbd97620fa31c778e6fc4f1fc54","tid":39173,"uid":65495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:27:03.000Z","msg":"MC 散景， MD Sharpness<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabab7120210e7656a5d5b6ce149bf0949811a08","tid":39173,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:08:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>MC 散景， MD Sharpness<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMC 同 MD 好多鏡一樣結構，只係改左coating 同鏡桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a114a7e955ebb37fad4e1de069352ee20c31565c","tid":39173,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:37:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有支MC 58.4 PF 同MC 28mm F/2.8<br />\n<br />\nbid緊支MD 35.8同MD 24/2.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我放緊MD 35/1.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無性趣"},{"pid":"3a68d22fc764f876233b5bf6f6e95df1e9f3888c","tid":39173,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T03:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有支MC 58.4 PF 同MC 28mm F/2.8<br />\n<br />\nbid緊支MD 35.8同MD 24/2.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我放緊MD 35/1.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無性趣</blockquote><br />\n無PM功能,可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ee42f37c0bef27c85da191ee7e543c2475f196","tid":39173,"uid":30351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:35:09.000Z","msg":"曾經做過fans，2010年買sony單反後，就 keep住用minolta a mount鏡，而家轉左會了。<br />\n<br />\nAF 35 F2<br />\nAF 80-200 2.8 G<br />\n有無人收養？"},{"pid":"b1c353cb9960a22f2977dbc52499f34bba974adc","tid":39173,"uid":63282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:20:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾經做過fans，2010年買sony單反後，就 keep住用minolta a mount鏡，而家轉左會了。<br />\n<br />\nAF 35 F2<br />\nAF 80-200 2.8 G<br />\n有無人收養？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2.8/80-200 G 白鏡係好嘢來，做乜咁諗唔開要放啊？<br />\n<br />\nBTW，2/35 叫咩價？"},{"pid":"1e0c7b2c4b5f742ab3fd95cbc46f95459a920cb8","tid":39173,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T18:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有支MC 58.4 PF 同MC 28mm F/2.8<br />\n<br />\nbid緊支MD 35.8同MD 24/2.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我放緊MD 35/1.8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有無性趣</blockquote><br />\n無PM功能,可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打我係肥花放緊，暫時得我一個唔係用白色背景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你試下PM我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f7534536207d1a2ec07060ee4952122d5e7452","tid":39173,"uid":17733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T22:21:50.000Z","msg":"用緊第2部Tc1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d944c047805876338c55961ea5af24511ee089","tid":39173,"uid":30351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>曾經做過fans，2010年買sony單反後，就 keep住用minolta a mount鏡，而家轉左會了。<br />\n<br />\nAF 35 F2<br />\nAF 80-200 2.8 G<br />\n有無人收養？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2.8/80-200 G 白鏡係好嘢來，做乜咁諗唔開要放啊？<br />\n<br />\nBTW，2/35 叫咩價？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我而家用nikon<br />\n幾好都無用😅<br />\n不如放比用家仲好<br />\n<br />\n35/2 $3000 我狗衝<br />\n開頭諗住a99ii出左會多啲人問<br />\n點知都係無人問津"},{"pid":"e43c283feb82d3a38a1047d4bc4fa25d68ad2b6b","tid":39173,"uid":50196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T17:01:56.000Z","msg":"push"}]}